### Understand the Components of a Good Password

![Image](/lot/asset/page/article/a-password-you-can-remember/850216.jpg)
 Photo by [Steve Johnson][3] from [Pexels][4].

Including all of the following components in your password will make it very difficult for someone to crack it:

 - Both upper-case and lower-case letters
 - Numbers
 - Symbols
 - At least 12 characters
 - Not easily decipherable as a real word or phrase upon first glance.

