### Select a Password Strategy

![Image](/lot/asset/page/article/a-password-you-can-remember/743986.jpg)
 Photo by [Jess Bailey Designs][9] from [Pexels][10].

You can apply one of the common password strategies mentioned above (e.g., removing vowels), or you can select your own.

 - Some experts even recommend finding several random words and stringing them together without modifying them past that
   point (e.g., “bananacoffeespoonphonecomfortercat”).

