### Add a Character that You Like to Your Password

![Image](/lot/asset/page/article/a-password-you-can-remember/20395259.jpg)
 Photo by [Jack Baghel][13] from [Pexels][14].

If you have a favorite character on your keyboard, replace a letter with it, or add it to the beginning of the password
to help remember it.

 - Most services require this step when creating a password.

