### Consider Doubling your Password

![Image](/lot/asset/page/article/a-password-you-can-remember/927629.jpg)
 Photo by [Tobias Dziuba][17] from [Pexels][18].

If your password is only at 8 characters and your selected service (e.g., Facebook) allows for 16 or more characters,
simply type the password twice.

 - For added security points, hold down the ⇧ Shift key while typing the second half of the password (e.g.,
   “h@r0ldh@r0ld” would become “h@r0ldH@R)LD”).

